data.name: txt_levelLoad0.Text
data.value:
As you destroy earth-bound meteoroids, you will probably attract the attention of the terrorists. Some of the ships you might encounter are:
Terrorist Wuss: This big blue-ish ship is the easiest to defeat. It's cowardly, stupid, and a poor shot.
Terrorist Hunter: This small green ship is agressive, quick, and accurate. It sports dual cannons and has a rapid rate of fire. Doesn't need shields.
Terrorist Seeker: This orange ship tries to stay far away from you, firing a cloud of long range seeking projectiles. If its shield goes down, it runs away.
Terrorist Scout: Probably the hardest to hit, but also weak offensively, this ship tries to stay alive long enough to call in reinforcements. It also has recharging shields.
